Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.95,0:01:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位久等了 漩涡鸣人拜见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你把丸铁带走的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子 你竟然破了我的网吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种软绵绵的网用力一咬就断了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 这个笼子你是咬不破的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把丸铁交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说没用了 听不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 挣脱不开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可惜 死的还是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.06,0:03:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修罗参见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,网里的小鬼知道宝藏的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 文殊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄哥哥…哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁 你刚刚叫他明雄是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那男孩到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫明雄的小孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的…亲弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我弟弟…我弟弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我弟弟已经死于那场大火了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他…他被你杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁不会杀人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁救了明雄哥哥还有我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五年前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对不忍的惨无人道寒了心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情不自禁地一把抱起了明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说话 这样会把烟吸进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果救了这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己也会有所改变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是多了几个和明雄一样遭遇的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了彻底瓦解不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想出了这次计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁 丸铁 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁 你没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的家庭都被不忍洗劫了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁用那些不忍抢来的钱财
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让明雄以哥哥的身份照顾这些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们以丸铁为中心 就像一家人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那刚才被困在那里的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁 你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去不忍的老窝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要救明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要救明雄的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你带我去老窝 其他别多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰 我理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是明雄和这些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是丸铁从不忍的手中救出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道不该有所表示吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此 丸铁依然是不忍的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的父母是被不忍杀死的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我犯得错无法弥补
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我救出明雄后任你处置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 这几个孩子交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五年来 我一直憎恨着他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在该如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 先救出你弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次 我一定会亲手救出明雄的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的宝藏在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的秘密基地在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面就是不忍的老窝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里就是首领修罗的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我估计明雄就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶旋风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给我处理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浓眉 就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄应该被关在地下室拷问呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他之前也是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚他会干些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先过去看看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞了半天才抓到一个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个小鬼真倔 死活不肯说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先杀了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再想办法找那些财宝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 你去追修罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里困不住我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种铁管算不了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰 这里交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多重影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰 快把明雄抱出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月雨血河
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这坏蛋 我不会放过你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁 原来你是为了保护明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁 把明雄交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 你真的来救我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄 撑着点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 真的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下不忍就全部消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漩涡鸣人参见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 小李
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄哥哥回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是明雄哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄哥哥 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 你受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧 一点小伤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 麻烦你帮明雄处理一下伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你添麻烦了 我们去京城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我实在无法原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你救了明雄也是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不忍全军覆没了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,押解中的丸铁也在混战中不幸丧生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了…万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想和丸铁他们在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是一个好哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你对那些孩子而言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却是不可缺少的大哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是当时未来得及给你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 各位忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家请多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁不在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怎么离开这座森林啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也不能回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条路已经走过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的肚子好饿 撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来救救我们啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 你在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是把伤员送进医院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.58,0:22:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不能随意带外人进村啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他绝不是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.02,0:22:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是他失忆了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.82,0:22:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是敌人安插的间谍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.65,0:22:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了 婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.90,0:22:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我特批了 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.45,0:22:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须对这个男孩全权负责
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.43,0:23:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
